President Donald J. Trump has authorized an extension of increased Federal funding for certain emergency protective measures in Puerto Rico. The extension includes 90 days of 100 percent Federal funding for emergency power restoration and 120 days for emergency temporary power support and Sheltering and Temporary Essential Power (STEP). For more information, media should contact the FEMA News Desk at (202) 646-3272 or FEMA-NEWS-DESK@FEMA.DHS.GOV.